&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-creativiry&#34;&gt;1 Creativiry&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To make your presentation unique, you need to be talented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What can you add:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Funny videos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Graphs and statistics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Memes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimalictic design.
















