&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-soft-skills&#34;&gt;3 Soft skills&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Very often the success of your talk is made not by the presentation itself, but by ability to deliver your thoughts to the audience. Practise and speak more to get rid of fear of public speeches and find out how to behave with the listeners correctly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good luck!
















